summary: 12 Best Anime Of 2018 So Far, Runner Ups, And Shows You Might Have Missed
title: 12 Best Anime Of 2018 So Far, Runner Ups, And Shows You Might Have Missed
body:
Anime keeps getting better every year. We’ve ranked our top picks for 2018, what are your favorites so far?

Saying an anime is the best involves a large amount of supposition. Each style of artwork and storytelling effects everyone differently. Once genres get incorporated, the whole “best of” might as well be tossed out the window. So, to keep things real, I submitted a varying number of polls for anime fans (casual and die-hard otaku) to express their favorite anime shows of 2018. And a few of the…
